{"tid":2514214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報「百句黨史名言」      毛澤東  習近平各佔30句","createTime":"2021-05-03T06:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:38:55.000Z","uid":204533,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"70fffffd3361fff7d3b52136c6a8e03b2461ed9c","tid":2514214,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"《人民日報》早前發布100句黨史名言錄，絕大部分出自中共五代領導人，<strong><span class=\"red\">已故領導人毛澤東和國家主席習近平的語錄各有30句，習近平在這次黨史名句中與毛澤東比肩</span></strong>；而中美關係緊張之際，其中<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">外界注意毛澤東1949年&ldquo;別了，司徒雷登&rdquo;文中&ldquo;中國人死都不怕，還怕困難嗎？</span></span></strong>&rdquo;分析認為，現今中美關係緊張、西方圍堵中國，重提這句話意有所指。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台報導，中共建黨百句名言，中共建政前有23句，建政後有77句。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百句名言中，<strong><span class=\"red\">鄧小平14句</span></strong>，江澤民和胡錦濤各十句；其餘六句則出自已故總理周恩來（2句）、已故國家主席劉少奇、已故中共中央委員會主席朱德、已故副總理陳雲和已故國防部長彭德懷，每人各一句。<br />\n<br />\n第一句是毛澤東1925年在&ldquo;中國社會各階級的分析&rdquo;提出的&ldquo;誰是我們的敵人？誰是我們的朋友？這個問題是革命的首要問題&rdquo;，最後一句是習近平今年在中共黨史學習教育動員大會講話中提出的&ldquo;江山就是人民，人民就是江山&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東上榜名言還包括&ldquo;槍桿子裡面出政權&rdquo;、&ldquo;星星之火，可以燎原&rdquo;、&ldquo;我們中華民族有同自己的敵人血戰到底的氣概&rdquo;、&ldquo;一切反動派都是紙老虎&rdquo;、&ldquo;中國人從此站立起來了&rdquo;、&ldquo;在戰略上要藐視敵人，在戰術上要重視敵人&rdquo;等。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，毛澤東在&ldquo;別了，司徒雷登&rdquo;一文中的&ldquo;中國人死都不怕，還怕困難嗎？&rdquo;也上榜。<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">這句話的全文是&ldquo;多少一點困難怕什麼。封鎖吧，封鎖十年八年，中國的一切問題都解決了。中國人死都不怕，還怕困難嗎？&rdquo;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分析認為，&ldquo;別了，司徒雷登&rdquo;是毛澤東於1949年8月18日在官媒新華社發表的文章，文中抨擊&ldquo;美國政府扶持支持中國國民黨發動內戰的政策&rdquo;，司徒雷登（John Leighton Stuart）是中華民國政府遷台前最後一任美國駐華大使。分析認為，現今中美關係緊張、西方圍堵中國，重提這句話意有所指。"},{"pid":"02ff8812f4bc66fd68b38df90c37a83f8fa559ac","tid":2514214,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20210502-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E7%99%BE%E5%8F%A5%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%B2%E5%90%8D%E8%A8%80-%E6%AF%9B%E6%BE%A4%E6%9D%B1-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%84%E4%BD%9430%E5%8F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20210502-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%258F%25A5%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E6%259D%25B1-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2590%2584%25E4%25BD%259430%25E5%258F%25A5&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=4a59c5ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20210502-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E7%99%BE%E5%8F%A5%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%B2%E5%90%8D%E8%A8%80-%E6%AF%9B%E6%BE%A4%E6%9D%B1-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%84%E4%BD%9430%E5%8F%A5</a>"},{"pid":"b180eb2c35e950be3f3ceb57b3cbd4e9137c2086","tid":2514214,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/4af907270d12fcde2d70ad7ad302f740.jpg/K57vptR7z8jTbh1_fCLtPrdm3rtgkK9so0gEWaNIBFk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F4af907270d12fcde2d70ad7ad302f740.jpg%2FK57vptR7z8jTbh1_fCLtPrdm3rtgkK9so0gEWaNIBFk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5fdad348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: HK01唔貼LINK"},{"pid":"7515ac85b3992e3eb680ccdc85cc72ce16d3f144","tid":2514214,"uid":281492,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"小學生名言：通商寬衣"},{"pid":"d8b8230e7d0c9c2cb34a935c297ef48dd21babb5","tid":2514214,"uid":44171,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"我在必不成功"},{"pid":"61743d8d54a48f2d28c9e5da6934503f822c1c72","tid":2514214,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"納dee名言呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3a3c5c56e0d8f8b1fdc7387b56dffe54418755","tid":2514214,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"以前資訊唔流通先鎖到国<br />\n而家點鎖<br />\n引發既恐慌同大逃亡規模同1949爭好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c483f690eeb39b49ff81e42b919bc520145111d","tid":2514214,"uid":280593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"人有多大膽"},{"pid":"aab0b34a70aa7c3a02ba2e3108c651300efc1b44","tid":2514214,"uid":139200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b180eb2c35e950be3f3ceb57b3cbd4e9137c2086","tid":2514214,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/4af907270d12fcde2d70ad7ad302f740.jpg/K57vptR7z8jTbh1_fCLtPrdm3rtgkK9so0gEWaNIBFk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F4af907270d12fcde2d70ad7ad302f740.jpg%2FK57vptR7z8jTbh1_fCLtPrdm3rtgkK9so0gEWaNIBFk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5fdad348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: HK01唔貼LINK"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"97...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牛頭角"},{"pid":"4f7fd4134e36465e40cfc9efe2f55694e8550b1b","tid":2514214,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"我什麼都不知道！"},{"pid":"984bc0080ec2c0a098e00cf42731514d9f6f9fde","tid":2514214,"uid":393145,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"97. 世上沒有從天而降的英雄， 只有挺身而出的凡人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華爾街狠人<br />\n2020年9月8日 &middot; <br />\n請廣傳！不要讓香港的抗爭歷史被篡改！￼<br />\n<br />\n習近平昨天在「抗疫慶典」裡用了一句過去一年香港抗爭的名句「世上沒有從天而降的英雄， 只有挺身而出的凡人」來稱讚在中国負責抗疫的前線青年醫護。<br />\n<br />\n真的相當諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n現在你在Google打「世上沒有從天而降的英雄， 只有挺身而出的凡人」你會見到中国媒體排山倒海地引用這句說話，更有一些媒體已經直接指這是中国抗疫成功的名句。可能唔使好耐，中国就會成功地把這句說話的來源寫成是「習近平的名句」。<br />\n<br />\n狠人用了些時間去考查這句說話的來源，發現最初是2015年，熱血公民李珏熙Marco Lee所創作的政治口號（現已舉家流亡海外*），當時未算被廣泛流傳；而首先第一次在香港抗爭中出現及被廣泛流傳呢句，是在2019年9月30日，在「國難五金」的老闊李政熙（李珏熙Marco Lee的哥哥）被香港警察打壓和拘捕，「國難五金」FB發表聲明，及在最後講了一句：<br />\n<br />\n「世上沒有從天而降的英雄，<br />\n只有挺身而出的凡人。」<br />\n<br />\n之後這聲明被廣泛流傳及轉發（原po已被刪除，但當時連登也有轉載該聲明：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606304</a>）。到10月和11月，有不同手足把這句說話分別寫在不同地方的連儂牆或街道上，用來勉勵和感謝每位前線手足在抗爭中的無私付出。<br />\n<br />\n咁幾時呢句說話出現在中国裡？ 就是武漢肺炎爆發初期，李文亮醫生因公開疫情被中共官員指控其造謠遭訓誡，他今年2月病死後，中国有網友開始用「世上沒有從天而降的英雄，只有挺身而出的凡人。」這句來悼念李文亮醫生。之後，這句說話開始流行於中国內，用來是讚揚抗疫醫護。<br />\n<br />\n到昨天，習近平首次公開引用這句說話，所有中国媒體，如獲至寶。<br />\n<br />\n狠人選擇把這歷史清晰哋寫出來，就是要以後的人永遠記得，「世上沒有從天而降的英雄，只有挺身而出的凡人」這句說話是因著中共暴政的荒謬而出現的，這記錄著暴政如何打壓香港人、如何因著隱瞞疫症而害死無數醫療和人民的生命。"},{"pid":"902b247e7344b8dfaf30aa0c2baa28983a595b31","tid":2514214,"uid":105166,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:08:25.000Z","msg":"頭兩句已經屌打CCtoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ac272b272a821723ec4955c34b1442acda60dd","tid":2514214,"uid":105166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"毛魔真係革命專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />句句都入肉"},{"pid":"d9f08d8eabe01ebb8c2200ed75e1a26090ccc5af","tid":2514214,"uid":189430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"這句不念"},{"pid":"c8420ba987fec321aa9a3fe5a6ea4797ec95ec76","tid":2514214,"uid":2654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"毛毛仲30句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家仲出得街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3318a3d4b3b9dfad026db5a8ce06544451f39dbd","tid":2514214,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8420ba987fec321aa9a3fe5a6ea4797ec95ec76","tid":2514214,"uid":2654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"毛毛仲30句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家仲出得街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"近平應該四十對二十<br />\n咁先顯得佢重要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae3b75893c36410019e35845b0e1a7c5a2f9531","tid":2514214,"uid":221731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"佢有乜可以同毛比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cee976f6cf1f25029e1a1bff8b5d4f0599c91b","tid":2514214,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>全部抄老衲</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccb16ef091c1a6ae85cc6d347574c9dece4bf90","tid":2514214,"uid":298186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">誰是我們的敵人？誰是我們的朋友？這個問題是革命的首要問題&rdquo;</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;星星之火，可以燎原&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;在戰略上要藐視敵人，在戰術上要重視敵人&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n真  <img src=\"/assets/fa